parameters:
Oh, what a nice fragrance... I thought it was my companions.
Welcome... Kufufufu...
It seems that humans have come... following a strange fate...

This is just a small corner of a vast dimension... And there are many
layers besides Rustium.

Originally, this is a place where humans would never have any
involvement in their lifetime... At most, it's good to enjoy it,
hehehe...

There's a little hot spring ahead. It's good for beauty, so it's nice
to soak slowly... Ufufufu.
